{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567380/extras/WLNOWGIF.gif?t=1740489548\" /><strong>Summary</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Luctus is an immersive story-based action-adventure game brought to life with a Pixel Art aesthetic. An in-depth experience filled with memorable characters and a rich universe awaits you. The game blends the dramatic story of our protagonist Nora with action-packed scenes and epic boss battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567380/extras/VillageHazirFixed.gif?t=1740489548\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A Dramatic Story</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Nora and Luna are two best friends who lost their parents at a young age. After the death of their father, these two young girls, who grew up under one roof, are on the hunt for a creature that caused his death. Nora's story begins when Luna disappears one morning and turns into a profound story of life and death.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567380/extras/Sarilma.gif?t=1740489548\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Epic Boss Battles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Epic boss battles are a must in any action game. Get ready for all-new and challenging action!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2567380/extras/simsizvideoClipchampileyapld-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1740489548\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A Fantastic Universe</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Luctus will allow you to experience a whole new and unique universe. New races, new realms, new creatures and new gods!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/sto